caption: The image is a poster featuring a gold crescent moon and a gold star of David. The text on the poster reads "Ramadan Kareem," which is a greeting for the Islamic holiday of Ramadan. The poster also includes a message wishing the recipient and their families with love, prosperity, and happiness. The image is tagged with "@reallygreatsite" and the year 1443 H.
original_title: Illustration Mosque and Month Ramadan Kareem Instagram Story
texts:
May Allah bless you & your
families with love, prosperity
& happines
